metadata.name: A whale's fate
metadata.description:
This piece commemorates the purchase of 1025 ETH by Tetranode at an average price of 1209$. The next bull run, ETH will hit 10k and this trade would have made the orca an almost net profit of 9 million $. 

This is the thesis of this project. Start our journey at the bottom in bear market and create value within the community towards the next bull run. 

It will be tough, but it will be fun.
